Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.71,0:00:09.70,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Let's create beautiful \Nharmonies together, Wakana.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.66,0:01:55.84,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.31,0:01:57.28,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.13,0:02:05.16,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Wakana!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:11.94,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:13.68,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:15.40,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I call an ambulance?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:19.86,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. I think it's just a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.23,0:02:21.74,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Have you taken medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:25.33,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:27.08,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:29.33,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Stay right there. I'll\Nmake up a bed downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:39.38,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:47.56,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:51.73,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me if you're in any pain at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:53.38,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:57.14,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Dora...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:06.87,Default,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 6\NLaughing and Remembering
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:09.35,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,The commencement of a new school year
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,means the all-too-short summer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:13.13,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,is once again coming to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you are still in the \Nspringtime of your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:19.38,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Ahead of you, hot summ—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:19.38,Episode Title,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Wakana isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:21.76,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher said she has a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:24.12,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You really think that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:27.22,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,She's been down for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:29.75,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you text her, \Nif you're so worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:31.89,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,And what if she doesn't respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:33.64,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's probably because you annoy—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.94,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Because she wants some time alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:49.66,Default,Car,0000,0000,0000,,Really? He says he's happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:51.09,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:52.80,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feeling better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:53.67,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,My fever's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:56.74,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I was sweating, so I'm gonna change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:57.63,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:03:59.97,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay home from \Nschool until next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:01.29,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:16.77,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:17.55,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:21.19,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Step one says that good vocalization \Ncomes from correct posture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:26.76,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Now use your glutes to \Nslowly lower yourself down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:33.66,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Miyamoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:41.86,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:45.13,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Exact change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:17.29,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:26.11,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:35.73,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.28,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Konatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.87,0:05:49.03,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:51.90,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:03.30,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing exciting, but here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:06.81,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa paid for half of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:07.93,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:12.51,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Your room's pretty empty, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:21.80,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Tatami's so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:23.57,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Reminds me of my grandpa's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:28.32,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Did I tell you how much he \Nloved the Condor Queens?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:30.27,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We sang their songs all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:34.49,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever he drank, he'd always \Ntalk about the concerts he went to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:40.17,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'd whine about how \Nmuch I wish I could've been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:44.75,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,And then, he'd promise \Nto take me to the next one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.57,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, it never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:51.57,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Promises should always be \Nkept, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:52.43,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:55.55,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I made a promise with my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She tried so hard to keep it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:03.81,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't. I was too \Nbusy thinking about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:07.82,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why she didn't \Ntell me she was sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:11.27,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,If only she'd told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:19.50,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You now, I'm actually glad it never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:22.85,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Once a promise is fulfilled, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:24.25,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,But since it's still out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it makes me think of my grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:29.26,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Like, "Rats! We never did it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:32.05,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,It's another precious memory of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.17,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What song's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:43.45,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's my song.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:45.18,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's my song?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.18,0:07:46.29,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:46.95,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.90,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have to make your own song.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:53.32,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't know how!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:55.82,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why don't we create your song together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:58.08,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:07:59.71,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:00.56,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:05.86,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wash these clothes \Nand get them back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:07.75,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,No rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:11.01,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Think people'll know I'm \Nnot wearing a bra?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:12.51,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Come visit us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:14.69,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:15.93,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:18.15,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat you to rice \Nflour dumplings next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:19.96,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:35.09,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Inbox
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:35.09,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}047 Okita Sawa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:35.09,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The Cake >_<
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:35.09,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}That Konatsu! "After I took the picture, \NWakana enjoyed the cake, I think," she wrote!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:35.09,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}She's not one bit sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:35.09,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'll make sure she gets it tomorrow at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:35.09,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Get well soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:35.09,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Can't wait to see you! <3 Cya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:42.27,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:42.27,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}My mom wants you to know, \N"that thing is done, so you \Ncan come pick it up anytime."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:42.27,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}That make sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:42.29,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,"That thing"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.84,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it in the shape of a penguin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:51.88,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Like I could!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:54.51,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.62,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,All right, have a good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:08:59.26,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,What about a heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.47,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:04.23,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:06.88,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:08.69,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:10.65,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:13.99,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:15.91,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You can have this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:21.79,Default,tape,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shirahamazaka Choir Competition \NFree Choice Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:19.09,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,A cassette tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:21.79,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,We recorded it before going to nationals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:24.51,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You can hear your mother's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:28.83,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you were such a cutie, \Nback in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:32.44,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,It's so sad. I hardly recognized you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:33.51,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Zip it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:40.61,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Wakana, are you free now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:45.29,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Hold the reins, grip the saddle,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and put your foot here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:48.78,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Your other foot, \Nor you'll end up backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:50.00,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:52.21,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,And, up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:57.20,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,It's so high!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:59.74,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Like seeing a different world, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:01.01,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:01.87,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:04.75,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Slowl—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:08.06,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Try to maintain your balance by squeezing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabure's sides with your thighs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.29,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:12.88,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Is Sabure your horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.13,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, he's my dad's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:19.01,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm riding him this year \Nin the mounted archery competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.06,0:10:22.68,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad was the person \Non the moped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:23.95,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:26.38,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't approve of me \Nbecoming an equestrian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:27.46,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,He says if I won't inherit \Nthe temple business,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be a government worker,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm not talking to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:37.04,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,But if, for some reason, \Nyou could never see him again,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your last conversation would be that fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:42.95,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Want to try jogging a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:45.26,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:49.16,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your back straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel his rhythm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:52.48,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pull on the reins; \Nrelax your arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:53.75,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:56.72,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,He's going too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:02.72,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that really works your muscles, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:03.96,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,My poor thighs...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:06.47,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Sabure just told me that he likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:07.39,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:09.98,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You should come ride him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:12.57,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:20.69,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:22.68,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:26.59,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Dora, where's Wakana?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:33.27,Default,Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to get some things \Ndone, so I'm leaving early.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:34.94,Default,Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Food's in the microwave.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:36.09,Default,Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}See you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:40.76,Default,bread,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}YumFluff Toast
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:09.49,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Sakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:20.88,Default,Book,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Start From Scratch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:20.88,Default,Book,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Vocal Training
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:20.88,Default,Book,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}<Beginner Edition>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:20.88,Default,Book,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Improve within moments!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:20.87,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I guess "Operation Secret Morning\N Practice to Surprise the Group" failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.07,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,You surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:27.39,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get better, so I \Ncan be useful to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:31.02,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana, what do you \Nthink we need most?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:32.71,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Common sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:35.69,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I told you there's no way \Nwe can improve on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:49.95,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:50.79,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:53.41,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're making a scary face \Nand going "Ah-ah!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:57.21,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, I'm trying to stay on pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:00.71,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have to treat voice exercises \Nlike they're a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:04.23,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Relax your shoulders, and look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:08.19,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sing as if you're trying \Nto tell someone you love,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who's far away, that you're \Ndoing well and having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:15.01,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:22.05,Default,Wein,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:23.82,Default,Wein,0000,0000,0000,,Emotion is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:26.23,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I guess a book can't teach you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:28.76,Default,Wein,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:32.43,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:33.48,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:36.42,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Ms. Takahashi had her baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:38.08,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she did?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:39.55,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:40.83,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:43.06,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka-kun, sorry I couldn't \Nstay and cheer for you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at your last badminton competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:45.83,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:47.41,Default,Wein,0000,0000,0000,,He lost, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:48.63,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:51.73,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what was she even doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:52.97,Default,Wein,0000,0000,0000,,Good question...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.71,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Compose
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.71,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Congrats on your new baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.71,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Please take good care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.71,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}From Sakai Wakana
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:00.71,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Send Mail
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:00.71,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}046 Ms. Takahashi
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:00.71,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sub: To Ms. Takahashi
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:00.71,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Congrats on your new baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:00.71,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Please take good care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:00.71,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}From Sakai Wakana
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:02.21,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sending message
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:02.63,text,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Your message has been sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:11.99,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,Sakai? Thanks for your message.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:14.08,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}School's over, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:14.97,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On your way home?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:15.75,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.22,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:19.01,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come over and see the baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.01,0:14:21.40,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,I also have a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.57,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know that gelato shop by the train station?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:25.24,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The one next to the Japanese candy store.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:26.97,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Their gelato is fantastic...{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:30.59,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:32.13,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:33.45,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:35.58,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had a chance \Nto go myself lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:36.97,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,Come in, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:38.44,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:43.70,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,So adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:56.37,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:58.03,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,Milk time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:01.06,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Babies are a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:02.52,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,She's cute now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:05.08,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,but it pains me to think \Nof how fast she'll grow
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into one of my loud-mouthed students.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:09.26,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Should a teacher be saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:11.45,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm off the clock right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:14.10,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, she doesn't have \Nto be perfectly-behaved,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so long as she's happy and healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:18.99,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,Want to hold her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:19.97,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:21.94,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay! I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:24.52,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:29.01,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,Just put your right arm close to your \Nside, and your left arm like so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:29.84,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Like so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:33.87,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana, dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:36.24,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.61,0:15:39.75,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,This here is what you call {\i1}food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:43.54,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hoping eating this will \Nmake you mend your lazy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shoving-bread-in-a-microwave-\Nand-calling-it-breakfast ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:49.85,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Today's your wedding anniversary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:51.68,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You remembered that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:55.01,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Mom said that because \Nit's close to my birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you just celebrated them \Ntogether after a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:00.93,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Did she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:03.59,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:09.34,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,How did you propose to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:10.55,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:11.65,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She proposed to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.78,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:15.40,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I should've asked mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:16.66,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:19.04,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It is the honest truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:23.75,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to brag and say \NI was a ladies' man, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:26.40,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:27.72,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Too salty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:32.73,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't Mom tell me she was sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:37.78,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,If she had, maybe we \Ncould've kept our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:40.10,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I would've been nicer to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:44.38,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom didn't want \Nyou to be nice to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:50.99,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can I say something selfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:56.30,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want you to tell Wakana \Nabout my illness just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:17:00.15,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She may be mature, \Nbut she gets sad too easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:01.82,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And her entrance exams are coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:04.27,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But she's not a child anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:10.01,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, it might actually hurt her not to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:11.48,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:18.14,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because we made a promise \Nto write a song together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:21.02,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She'll understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just explain it to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then you can write—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:26.01,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A sad song about saying goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:31.20,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By writing a song together,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel like I can leave \Npart of me in her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:41.91,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want it to be full of \Nsadness, but kindness and strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.23,0:17:45.47,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Long after I'm gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that song will be there for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:54.27,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She can think of me whenever she hears it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:17:59.68,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Remember how you rushed to the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}without even closing the store, \Nwhen Wakana was born?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:04.34,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:06.65,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She was still faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:09.40,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's always been impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:13.62,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you remember what you said \Nwhen you first saw her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:19.52,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can never tell her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:24.44,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so glad she grew up loving music.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:27.71,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My precious little girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:31.95,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll never leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:36.36,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:50.42,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,She loved me so much, and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't understand... I threw it all away...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:59.08,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,The memories... The \Npiano... The music...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:06.45,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana, can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:09.43,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:16.05,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:20.43,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She'd taken some notes for the song
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she wanted to write with \Nyou once exams were over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:26.75,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But then she was gone so fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:30.66,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I've been holding on to these,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,waiting for you to \Ncome to terms with things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:42.50,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything \Nabout music, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you could continue it, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:50.83,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'd also like the hear the \Nsong you wrote together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:53.29,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,There's this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:57.66,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want it, I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:58.69,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:00.51,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't throw away \Nsuch an important keepsake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:01.75,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,And the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:04.39,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,How could I get rid of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom used it to propose to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:11.85,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Liar...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:17.04,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Think I could leave it in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:18.81,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Might be a bit cramped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.99,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:26.03,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind if I take a look at this first?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:27.70,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:28.93,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start eating without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:37.56,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:06.67,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Recording, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:08.69,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We will now commence singing—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.69,0:21:10.43,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Too awkward, Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:11.87,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mahiru...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:13.64,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll now sing a song
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}born between Nao and me, \Nand nurtured by our choir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:15.22,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.66,0:21:31.49,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A fresh wind races through \Nthe grass and leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.49,0:21:38.94,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The view is clear, \Nas far as the eye can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:47.16,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And now, a graceful light is flooding,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:55.77,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}softly illuminating everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.96,0:22:01.44,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if you can't see the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:04.95,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}because of the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.95,0:22:09.75,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the future you're dreaming of
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.75,0:22:12.26,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is still right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.26,0:22:16.70,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you muster your courage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.70,0:22:20.29,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to take a step forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:24.77,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want you to remember
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.77,0:22:32.74,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the days we spent with sparkling eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:40.30,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's sing every day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:44.14,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with all our hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.14,0:22:48.63,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}our song echoing to the skies,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:51.50,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.50,0:22:55.95,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if it should ever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:22:59.68,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}reach you again somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:04.02,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want you to remember
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.02,0:23:11.99,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the days we spent with sparkling eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.99,0:23:20.51,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the days we spent with beaming smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:34.62,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You probably don't understand \Nbecause you lack experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.62,0:23:35.89,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,It's not love!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:37.42,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Girls are scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:40.60,Episode Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 7 \NSpinning in Circles and Losing Sight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.42,0:23:38.50,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Sai, are you coming, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.50,0:23:40.60,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Is liking it not enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.00,0:24:02.00,Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,
